.TH ABRAFLEXI-REMINDER-CLEAN-LABELS 1 "" "abraflexi-reminder" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi\-reminder\-clean\-labels \- remove reminder labels from fully-paid customers in AbraFlexi
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-reminder-clean-labels
[\fB\-e\fR|\fB\-\-environment\fR \fIENV_FILE\fR]
[\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR \fIFILE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scans all customers in AbraFlexi and removes the UPOMINKA1, UPOMINKA2,
UPOMINKA3, and NEPLATIC labels from customers that have no outstanding
overdue invoices.
.PP
Results are written as JSON to standard output or to the file specified with
\fB\-o\fR/\fB\-\-output\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-e ", " \-\-environment " " \fIFILE\fR
Path to environment file (default: \fI../.env\fR).
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Write JSON result to \fIFILE\fR instead of standard output.
.SH FILES
.I /etc/abraflexi-reminder/reminder.env
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-reminder (1),
.BR abraflexi-reminder-init (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
